    "en": {
      "title": "The risk of dengue increases",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The National Dengue Control Unit of the Ministry of Health states that due to the rainy weather, there is a risk of dengue fever spreading further.",
        "The Dengue Control Unit also said that 1304 dengue fever cases have been found in 23 districts across the country in the past week.",
        "The unit also says that Dehiwala, Homagama, Kaduwela, Maharagama, Colombo city, Battaramulla, Egodauyana and Gothatuwa are high risk areas where dengue spreads rapidly."
      ],
